title: Beekeepers Daughter Raw Buckwheat Blossom Honey by the Beekeeper's Daughter - 2.5 lb Jar (2.5 pound)…
features: All of the Beekeepers Daughter’s honey is raw & unfiltered, so the honey remains just the way it was in the hive. Hand bottled into 16oz. (1lb) Glass Wide Mouth Jars to easily scoop the honey out.
The Beekeeper's Daughter Raw Buckwheat honey is delicately harvested from the bloom of the buckwheat plant.
Raw Buckwheat Honey has a deep, dark brown, malty earth flavor and is high in mineral content and antioxidant compounds.
The Beekeeper's Daughter raw honey is full of pollen, enzymes, vitamins, minerals, and aroma. It can contain bits of pollen and propolis. Right from the hive to your table.
In time all raw honey will naturally crystallize. Crystallized honey does not compromise in taste or nutritional value. To liquefy place the container into a pot of hot water.
